  "title": "[ Perm Private Hospital Staff Nurse ] Operating Theatre NO NEED EXP #HYT",
  "description": "<p><strong>Staff Nurse (Operating Theatre)</strong></p>\n<p><br>\n<strong>Location:</strong> Central<br>\n<strong>Contract Type:</strong> Permanent</p>\n<h3>Working Hours</h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>3 Rotating Shifts</li>\n  <li>Any 5 days per week</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Job Responsibilities</h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>Assist in peri-operative care and support procedures in the Operating Theatre.</li>\n  <li>Maintain sterile environment and adhere to surgical protocols.</li>\n  <li>Provide assistance to surgeons, anesthetists, and other OT team members during operations.</li>\n  <li>Ensure proper handling and documentation of instruments and patient records.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Requirements</h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>Valid nursing certification and registration required.</li>\n  <li>No prior OT experience needed; candidates with inpatient ward experience are welcome to apply.</li>\n  <li>No need experience , training provided; candidates with internship experience are welcome to apply.</li>\n  <li>Willing and able to commit to rotating shift schedules.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>All qualified applicants, please<strong> click “ APPLY NOW”</strong></p>\n<p>Or you may send in your resume to:</p>\n<p><strong>Whatsapp: </strong><u><strong>https://wa.me/+6597430026</strong></u></p>\n<p><strong>Email : </strong><a href=\"mailto:kimlow@recruitexpress.com.sg\"><u><strong>kimlow@recruitexpress.com.sg</strong></u></a></p>\n<p>Kimmy Low Yi Ting (Kim) | CEI Registration Number: R23112122</p>\n<p>Recruit Express Pte Ltd Company Reg. No. 199601303W | EA LICENCE Number: 99C4599</p>",
